<tr id="L323"><td><a href="#L323">323</a></td><td>DUKAT:  Well done. Well, Major, quite a prize we've taken. The first Klingon bird of prey ever to be captured by Cardassia.</td></tr>

<tr id="L324"><td><a href="#L324">324</a></td><td>KIRA:  I think I just found a bigger prize. It looks like we've got the target priorities of all Klingon raiders in Cardassian space.</td></tr>

<tr id="L325"><td><a href="#L325">325</a></td><td>DUKAT:  I'll contact Central Command and inform them of our success. I think I'll request my Legate title be reinstated, effective immediately. Get me Central Command. No, on second thought, this is too important for them. I want to speak to the Chairman of the Detepa Council himself on a secure channel.</td></tr>

<tr id="L326"><td><a href="#L326">326</a></td><td>DAMAR:  I can't do that from here, sir. The communication terminals on the bridge are down but I could re-route it to the Captain's quarters.</td></tr>

